## API Endpoint

### Create Collection Link

**Endpoint:** `POST /v1/gateway/api/create`

**Request Headers:**
```json
{
  "Content-Type": "application/json"
}
```

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "accessKey": "bd60c4368cce7b5e33f52de59b27649eb96ee85919ec804734a0f8a722bbcc9c",
  "partnerCode": "PAY2SLNASDTFCHN7JVB3",
  "partnerName": "Comvia",
  "requestId": "uuid-string",
  "amount": "1100000",
  "orderId": "1234567890",
  "orderInfo": "Nap tien Comvia",
  "orderType": "pay2s",
  "bankAccounts": [
    {
      "account_number": "1234567890",
      "bank_id": "ACB"
    }
  ],
  "redirectUrl": "https://yourdomain.com/return",
  "ipnUrl": "https://yourdomain.com/webhooks/pay2s/ipn",
  "requestType": "pay2s",
  "signature": "hmac-sha256-signature",
  "lang": "vi"
}
```

**Response (Success):**
```json
{
  "resultCode": 0,
  "resultMessage": "Success",
  "qrList": [
    {
      "qrCode": "data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAA...",
